  <source>Novartis</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of this research study is to evaluate, in the open-label extension phase, the safety
      and efficacy of the rivastigmine transdermal patch in patients with probable Alzheimer's
      Disease
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
